{"tid":2163116,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專訪蔡霞： 「換領導人是大家普遍的想法」","createTime":"2020-08-18T13:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T04:53:59.000Z","uid":53062,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"50a485958824a87337971264b27328da261b131f","tid":2163116,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8AqcbSQ_LjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8AqcbSQ_LjM&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5k63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=a3847d7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8AqcbSQ_LjM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中央黨校周一（17日）公布，其退休教授蔡霞發表「有嚴重政治問題和損害國家聲譽」的言論，嚴重違反黨的政治紀律，決定開除其黨籍。<br />\n<br />\n本台普通話組華盛頓記者唐家婕第一時間聯繫了身在美國的蔡霞，詳談外界關心的問題，包括中共黨內對撤換習近平的看法、習近平控制黨員幹部的手法等。<br />\n<br />\n詳細報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/325eXqq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F325eXqq&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5k63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=1932457f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/325eXqq</a>"},{"pid":"ba13e668071854d37f3ed02c496525cd2d896bd1","tid":2163116,"uid":1781,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"50a485958824a87337971264b27328da261b131f","tid":2163116,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8AqcbSQ_LjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8AqcbSQ_LjM&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5k63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=a3847d7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8AqcbSQ_LjM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中央黨校周一（17日）公布，其退休教授蔡霞發表「有嚴重政治問題和損害國家聲譽」的言論，嚴重違反黨的政治紀律，決定開除其黨籍。<br />\n<br />\n本台普通話組華盛頓記者唐家婕第一時間聯繫了身在美國的蔡霞，詳談外界關心的問題，包括中共黨內對撤換習近平的看法、習近平控制黨員幹部的手法等。<br />\n<br />\n詳細報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/325eXqq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F325eXqq&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5k63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=1932457f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http